// ── Preteritum-form regression (Phase 05.1-05 post-hoc) ──
// Regression case: `Kan gikk på skolen` — user smoke test 2026-04-21 found
// modal_form silent on preteritum-form main verb in the browser.
// Root cause: vocab-seam-core.buildIndexes previously fed wordList
// (feature-gated by popup's "basic" preset which excludes grammar_preteritum)
// into buildLookupIndexes, so verbInfinitive.get('gikk') was undefined.
// Fixture harness passes `() => true` so it missed this; these cases exist
// to keep the full-superset spell-check path honest even when the feature
// gate regression pattern re-emerges. See the vocab-seam-core.js comment
// on buildIndexes for the fix rationale (unfiltered wordList for spell-check
// lookup indexes, feature-gated wordList for word-prediction).
